    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the clinic is so expensive and busy though... i just want to manage this at home for now. i read online that sometimes for really bad inflammation, people take it more frequently so it stays at a steady level in their system. wouldn't taking one every 2 hours be better than waiting 6 hours and having it wear off? i'm just trying to avoid the pain coming back.",
